body.p:
        Usage:
        ... in "build.json" define your properties like this:

"properties": {
    "buildDir": {
        "?os.platform=windows": "target",
        "?os.platform=unix": "unixtarget"
    }
}

        Add to new phase to "build.json":

"copySomething": {
    "copy": {
        "from": ["build.json"],
        "to": "$(buildDir)/"
    }
}

        Remember this phase should go inside "phases" object (valid JSON applies).

        Execute this phase only:

uisdk-build copySomething

        Once executed verify the name of folder into which "build.json" was
        copied during "copySomething" phase.
